<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA512_03_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_01.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_02.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_03.css" />

    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema512_02_0004.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_03_su_0004" data-current-page="page_3">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_green" lang="y">곱셈식을 이용하여 3을 몇 배 한 수를 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="const_cover">
          <div class="input_area const_cover">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">곱셈식을 완성해 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="question_box">
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span lang="y">3을 1배 한 수 </span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA512_03_SU/0006_contents_1.png" alt="arrow icon" class="ml_8"/>
                  <span class="ml_8">3&times;1=3</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span lang="y">3을 2배 한 수</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA512_03_SU/0006_contents_1.png" alt="arrow icon" class="ml_8"/>
                  <span class="ml_8">3&times;2=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center">
                  <span lang="y">3을 3배 한 수</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA512_03_SU/0006_contents_1.png" alt="arrow icon" class="ml_8" />
                  <span class="ml_8">3&times;</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                  <span>&#8942;</span>
                  <span>&#8942;</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">3을 1배, 2배, 3배 한 수를 각각 써 보세요.</h3>
              <div class="question_box gap_12">
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  ,
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  ,
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="9"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
              <div class="summarize_wrap">
                <div class="summarize promise">
                  <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">3을 1배, 2배, 3배, ... 한 수인 3, 6, 9, ...를 </span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="3의 배수" lang="y" onclick="countClick();">3의 배수</button>
                    <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">이와 같이 어떤 수를 1배, 2배, 3배, ... 한 수를</span>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">그 수의</span>
                    <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="배수" lang="y" onclick="countClick();">배수</button>
                    <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="etc_img">
                    <p lang="y">어떤 수의 배수는 셀 수 없이 많아요.</p>
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA512_02_SU/0009_contents_3.png"
                      alt="어떤 수의 약수에는 1과 자기자신이 항상 포함돼요. 라고 말하는 선생님 그림" />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset" lang="y">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck" lang="y">확인</button>
          <button class="btnCheck etcImgOn" lang="y" onclick="addInfoImg()">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
